    "description": "<br><br>Hyper Simon X是一款街机射击解谜游戏，巧妙地将SHMUP机制与经典怀旧的“西蒙说”记忆游戏相结合。当你按照精确的顺序摧毁敌人时，准备迎接前所未有的挑战！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878180/extras/281fb1633218327ca7c587f4758a6486.poster.avif?t=1762273957\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878180/extras/281fb1633218327ca7c587f4758a6486.webm?t=1762273957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878180/extras/281fb1633218327ca7c587f4758a6486.mp4?t=1762273957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在Hyper Simon X中，通过熟练地按照显示的顺序摧毁船只来升级，每个级别呈现出像西蒙说一样的越来越长的序列。通过摧毁其他船只并遵循序列来获得组合，从而增加您的得分。请注意潜在的危险，如与其他船只的碰撞，避开来袭的子弹，并避免用特殊射击击中错误的颜色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878180/extras/c2283248215ecd177f1500fa500f2c1b.poster.avif?t=1762273957\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878180/extras/c2283248215ecd177f1500fa500f2c1b.webm?t=1762273957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878180/extras/c2283248215ecd177f1500fa500f2c1b.mp4?t=1762273957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>沉浸在终极吃币街机体验中，具有复古像素艺术图形，提供键盘，鼠标或游戏手柄无缝游戏体验，伴随着令人赞叹的原声音轨。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878180/extras/db8b8df942f1165c3293aaf3413c2185.poster.avif?t=1762273957\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878180/extras/db8b8df942f1165c3293aaf3413c2185.webm?t=1762273957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/878180/extras/db8b8df942f1165c3293aaf3413c2185.mp4?t=1762273957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hyper Simon X基于我为Ludum Dare 41制作的免费游戏“Hiper Simox 3000”，该活动的主题是将两种不兼容的流派结合起来。",
